    "description": "《电钻少女》讲述了一段紧张刺激的海盗冒险之旅，故事的主角名叫佩珀，是一个对勘探满怀热情的海魂少女；她手中挥舞的是研磨枪，那是她超强力的钻孔装置。<br><br>遭遇海难后，佩珀的宝藏被洗劫一空，如今她必须发动手中值得信赖的武器，夺回淘气的纳林斯偷走的东西。手持研磨枪的佩珀可以在各类地形和水面中钻进钻出，还能控制机器，用各种异想天开的方式粉碎任何胆敢阻拦她的敌人，直到她找回自己应得的财富——连本带息都找回来！<br><br>只不过，佩珀的进展并没有想象中顺利，因为阴影中开始有神秘生物不断浮现……<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076580/extras/21d33abcf9473034e9ce5a8ccc759362.poster.avif?t=1752168250\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076580/extras/21d33abcf9473034e9ce5a8ccc759362.webm?t=1752168250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076580/extras/21d33abcf9473034e9ce5a8ccc759362.mp4?t=1752168250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >砂石遍地的游戏之旅</h2>施展精确的移动、流畅的钻探和刺激的飞跃，你将在栩栩如生、色彩斑斓的世界中翱翔。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076580/extras/fda85ae81bbca95baa8b966616e5c47e.poster.avif?t=1752168250\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076580/extras/fda85ae81bbca95baa8b966616e5c47e.webm?t=1752168250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076580/extras/fda85ae81bbca95baa8b966616e5c47e.mp4?t=1752168250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >钻进钻出好不刺激</h2>研磨枪在手，钻遍世界无敌手。你还能发现新的钻头，让混乱程度更上层楼，同时还能揭开更巧妙的谜题。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076580/extras/0c0454aa91f9b1b1b94da0fa3ab5a590.poster.avif?t=1752168250\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076580/extras/0c0454aa91f9b1b1b94da0fa3ab5a590.webm?t=1752168250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076580/extras/0c0454aa91f9b1b1b94da0fa3ab5a590.mp4?t=1752168250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >征服与收集</h2>在冒险过程中，你将拾获珠宝和其他的宝物，在商店变现后即可为佩珀购买升级能力、在世界地图上开辟新路径，还能为你的贴纸簿收集典藏版贴纸。",
